    • editProject

      public void editProject​(Company company, Scanner sc, int choice, Project project)
      editProject Method.
      The method is used to edit an existing project
      Parameters:
      company - Company object which stores the projects and people
      sc - Scanner object to take in user inputs
      choice - Integer reflecting index of which project the user chose to edit
      project - Project object of the actual project to be edited

      version 1.00
